          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1699376198412-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1699376198412-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is marinating, chop your<strong> chives </strong>finely</p><p>Combine the<strong> chopped chives</strong> and <strong>half </strong>your <strong>soured cream</strong> in a small bowl with <strong>half</strong> of the<strong> remaining cider vinegar </strong>(you’ll use the rest later!), the <strong>remaining grated garlic</strong>, a splash of<strong> cold water</strong> and a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>ranch dressing</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>carrot & cabbage slaw mix</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>remaining soured cream </strong>and <strong>remaining cider vinegar </strong>– this is your<strong> slaw</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1699376201826-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
