            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>cornflour</strong> to a large bowl with 40g <span class=\"text-purple\">[60g]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[80g]</span><strong> flour</strong>, <strong>ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>dried</strong> <strong>oregano</strong>, <strong>ground coriander </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>spice mix</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>marinated chicken</strong> to the spice mix and mix well until evenly coated – this is your <strong>coated chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1699376210286-x200.jpg",
