            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1699376217575-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve your <strong>fried chicken </strong>with the<strong> slaw</strong>, <strong>BBQ beans </strong>and <strong>fries </strong>to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>ranch dressing </strong>over the fries and top with the <strong>crispy bacon</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
